      <odd id="aspace_9f417130c7b58afbcc4fca579fe1f790">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 46-B (YRG 46-B), Records and materials documenting individual Yale buildings, facilities, and grounds.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_2ed3308cb04c1be08b44b725eaa46675">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Harvey Cushing/John Hay Whitney Medical Library, 1990.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
