      <prefercite id="aspace_adb3b2d722a6a267eed4a19368faa21e">
         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Harvey Cushing/John Hay Whitney Medical Library, Yale University, Renovation Records (RU 6). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <arrangement id="aspace_ff51b92ba38c2e6034e9e5ab4ce29620">
         <head>Arrangement</head>
         <p>The records are arranged alphabetically by subject.</p>  
      </arrangement>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_5db8568148af7e42416726afa0dc160a">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of files of the Harvey Cushing/John Hay Whitney Medical Library at Yale concerning planning, budgets, furniture, contractors, gifts, systems, and the dedication of the renovated library.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
      <accessrestrict id="aspace_bd1693c55a87a952a60e52a05400f49e">
         <head>Conditions Governing Access</head>
         <p>Some records in this finding aid have been redacted, as they include student names, donor names, and other restricted data. These records will not appear in the published finding aid.</p>  
      </accessrestrict>
